description: Muslim Guide Skill app tells you prayer times, open (azan/athan). It allow you to set a default location so next time you ask for prayer times you don't have to say the location.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask muslim guide prayer times for Chicago
Alexa, ask muslim guide what's my next prayer time
name: Muslim Guide
